{"pagelen": 100, "values": [{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1130/comments/9332082.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/1130#comment-9332082"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1130.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 1130, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}ts=1694483"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gazebo", "full_name": "osrf/gazebo", "uuid": "{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}"}, "title": "Camera sensors not updated without shadows (and directional light) in scence"}, "content": {"raw": "Sorry, I was not logged in. You are welcome to contact me for further details.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Sorry, I was not logged in. You are welcome to contact me for further details.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2014-03-26T15:26:49.291709+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Andreas Bihlmaier", "uuid": "{5937f01e-6c0d-4cfd-b8d2-6276f312c74c}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5937f01e-6c0d-4cfd-b8d2-6276f312c74c%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5937f01e-6c0d-4cfd-b8d2-6276f312c74c%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0a70ca141ff43b3d9385a1823f4c265ed=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsAB-3.png"}}, "nickname": "andreasBihlmaier", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:32bae45c-b312-4f18-8f77-d15bd9d6f68b"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 9332082}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1130/comments/9340310.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/1130#comment-9340310"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1130.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 1130, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}ts=1694483"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gazebo", "full_name": "osrf/gazebo", "uuid": "{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}"}, "title": "Camera sensors not updated without shadows (and directional light) in scence"}, "content": {"raw": "Can you provide a link to a world file that illustrates this problem? I didn't see any clickable links on the ros answers page.\n\nAs an aside, I tried deleting the sun to help reproduce this, but apparently that's a bad idea (#1133).", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Can you provide a link to a world file that illustrates this problem? I didn't see any clickable links on the ros answers page.</p>\n<p>As an aside, I tried deleting the sun to help reproduce this, but apparently that's a bad idea (<a href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/1133/trying-to-delete-sun-causes-gzclient-seg\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Trying to delete sun causes gzclient seg-fault\" class=\"ap-connect-link\"><s>#1133</s></a>).</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2014-03-26T23:34:57.983170+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 9340310}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1130/comments/9345367.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/1130#comment-9345367"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1130.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 1130, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}ts=1694483"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gazebo", "full_name": "osrf/gazebo", "uuid": "{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}"}, "title": "Camera sensors not updated without shadows (and directional light) in scence"}, "content": {"raw": "You can find an example world file [here](https://gist.github.com/andreasBihlmaier/9802981).\nYou also need the [model camera_ros](https://gist.github.com/andreasBihlmaier/9803002) (although you might be one of the last persons that needs this information, perhaps others want to test it, too: simply copy model.sdf and model.config to ~/.gazebo/models/camera_ros).\n\nIf you start gazebo (rosrun gazebo_ros gazebo camera_shadows_problem.xml) and watch the image topic (e.g. rqt Image View plugin) everything is fine (the pendulum is moving in gzclient and the camera stream).\nNow disable shadows (GUI: Scene -> shadows [ ] False), the camera stream stops.\nIf you reenable the shadows the camera stream will also start again.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>You can find an example world file <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"https://gist.github.com/andreasBihlmaier/9802981\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>.\nYou also need the <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"https://gist.github.com/andreasBihlmaier/9803002\" rel=\"nofollow\">model camera_ros</a> (although you might be one of the last persons that needs this information, perhaps others want to test it, too: simply copy model.sdf and model.config to ~/.gazebo/models/camera_ros).</p>\n<p>If you start gazebo (rosrun gazebo_ros gazebo camera_shadows_problem.xml) and watch the image topic (e.g. rqt Image View plugin) everything is fine (the pendulum is moving in gzclient and the camera stream).\nNow disable shadows (GUI: Scene -&gt; shadows [ ] False), the camera stream stops.\nIf you reenable the shadows the camera stream will also start again.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2014-03-27T08:38:20.931912+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Andreas Bihlmaier", "uuid": "{5937f01e-6c0d-4cfd-b8d2-6276f312c74c}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5937f01e-6c0d-4cfd-b8d2-6276f312c74c%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5937f01e-6c0d-4cfd-b8d2-6276f312c74c%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0a70ca141ff43b3d9385a1823f4c265ed=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsAB-3.png"}}, "nickname": "andreasBihlmaier", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:32bae45c-b312-4f18-8f77-d15bd9d6f68b"}, "updated_on": "2014-03-27T08:39:47.347164+00:00", "type": "issue_comment", "id": 9345367}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1130/comments/9917039.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/1130#comment-9917039"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1130.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 1130, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}ts=1694483"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gazebo", "full_name": "osrf/gazebo", "uuid": "{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}"}, "title": "Camera sensors not updated without shadows (and directional light) in scence"}, "content": {"raw": "An important update:\nIt seems the camera image is only influenced by the directional light source and scene settings (e.g. ambient), but not by other light sources.\nThat is, if you add a point light your gz_client will show quite different images compared to the simulated camera - which I guess is unintended.\n\nIMHO the goal for the simulated camera should be to show everything as in gz_client, of course without the GUI specific elements (arrows etc).\n\nNote: I did not yet investigate the rendering path (gazebo / gazebo / rendering / Camera.cc) myself.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>An important update:\nIt seems the camera image is only influenced by the directional light source and scene settings (e.g. ambient), but not by other light sources.\nThat is, if you add a point light your gz_client will show quite different images compared to the simulated camera - which I guess is unintended.</p>\n<p>IMHO the goal for the simulated camera should be to show everything as in gz_client, of course without the GUI specific elements (arrows etc).</p>\n<p>Note: I did not yet investigate the rendering path (gazebo / gazebo / rendering / Camera.cc) myself.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2014-04-30T09:23:09.147456+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Andreas Bihlmaier", "uuid": "{5937f01e-6c0d-4cfd-b8d2-6276f312c74c}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5937f01e-6c0d-4cfd-b8d2-6276f312c74c%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5937f01e-6c0d-4cfd-b8d2-6276f312c74c%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0a70ca141ff43b3d9385a1823f4c265ed=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsAB-3.png"}}, "nickname": "andreasBihlmaier", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:32bae45c-b312-4f18-8f77-d15bd9d6f68b"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 9917039}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1130/comments/10908633.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/1130#comment-10908633"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1130.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 1130, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}ts=1694483"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gazebo", "full_name": "osrf/gazebo", "uuid": "{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}"}, "title": "Camera sensors not updated without shadows (and directional light) in scence"}, "content": {"raw": "I'm unable to reproduce this bug in gazebo 3(.1) (actually compiled from branch set_joint_position).\nCameras work with or without directional light and with or without shadows.\n\nI guess this can be closed.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I'm unable to reproduce this bug in gazebo 3(.1) (actually compiled from branch set_joint_position).\nCameras work with or without directional light and with or without shadows.</p>\n<p>I guess this can be closed.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2014-06-25T10:45:25.943851+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Andreas Bihlmaier", "uuid": "{5937f01e-6c0d-4cfd-b8d2-6276f312c74c}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5937f01e-6c0d-4cfd-b8d2-6276f312c74c%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5937f01e-6c0d-4cfd-b8d2-6276f312c74c%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0a70ca141ff43b3d9385a1823f4c265ed=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsAB-3.png"}}, "nickname": "andreasBihlmaier", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:32bae45c-b312-4f18-8f77-d15bd9d6f68b"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 10908633}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1130/comments/10914794.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/1130#comment-10914794"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1130.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 1130, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}ts=1694483"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gazebo", "full_name": "osrf/gazebo", "uuid": "{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}"}, "title": "Camera sensors not updated without shadows (and directional light) in scence"}, "content": {"raw": "There were some recent pull requests to fix lighting (pull request #1110, pull request #1094, and pull request #1088). Perhaps one of those helped to fix it.\n\nI'm marking as fixed, please re-open if the problem persists.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>There were some recent pull requests to fix lighting (<a href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1110/fix-updating-light-properties-in-world\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">pull request #1110</a>, <a href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1094/fix-deleting-and-saving-light-on-server\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">pull request #1094</a>, and <a href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1088/fix-deleting-sun\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">pull request #1088</a>). Perhaps one of those helped to fix it.</p>\n<p>I'm marking as fixed, please re-open if the problem persists.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2014-06-25T16:05:36.302093+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 10914794}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1130/comments/30610547.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/1130#comment-30610547"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1130.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 1130, "repository": {"link